<br>
Here's my suggestion for changing this spell...please make it summon a full quiver. Why summon a quiver with only three stacks? I ended up casting the spell twice every time, destroying the second quiver and putting the rest of the stacks in the first one.<br>
<br>
The same I would suggest for our other summoned ranged items...Pouch of Quellious and Bandoleer of Luclin.<br>
<br>
Izudin<br>
