<br>
Think of it this way:<br>
Spell summons Quiver + Arrows1 + Arrows2 + Arrows3.<br>
You summon a quiver, and place the stacks of arrows vertically down the left hand side, then summon a second quiver (destroying the quiver itself) and place the arrows vertically down the right hand side.<br>
<br>
You end up with a Quiver stacked like this:<!--EZCODE CODE START--><pre> 
|-----------------|
| Quiver of Marr  |
|-----------------|
|Arrows1 | Arrows1|
|-----------------|
|Arrows2 | Arrows2|
|-----------------|
|Arrows3 | Arrows3|
|-----------------|</pre><!--EZCODE CODE END-->Now summon a third quiver, but only keep the first stack of arrows (Arrow1), hand the quiver and the arrows to the Ranger, and get him to use them.  If the Ranger puts the 7th stack of Arrows (type Arrow1) into the Ammo slot, when they run out it will move the arrows from the top left corner of the quiver to their ammo slot automatically, then do the same with the top right stack of arrows as they are all the same type.<br>
<br>
However, once the top right stack has been moved to the ammo slot and exhausted, it will tell the ranger he is out of ammo even though he has 4 stacks of arrows with the same name left in his Quiver.<br>
<br>
You can verify this yourself by using Bandoleer of Luclin (as Magicians can throw knives, but cannot use a bow and arrow).  It suffers the same problems.<br>
<br>
I haven't played with them in quite some as due to this limitation my Ranger friends just used their Tolans Bracer, because it summons one stack at a time and they are all the same type so they all flow seemlessly from the Quiver to their ammo slot. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Now they all have Endless Quiver, so it's a mute point.  I did bug rep it long ago, with any luck it's been fixed, but I wouldn't count on it. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style=""><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59365">Kathodos</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Battle Cleric of Tunare - Tholuxe Paells</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style=""><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59365">Kantreach</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Arch Mage Antagonist - Tholuxe Paells</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showPrevMessage?topicID=1642.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showNextMessage?topicID=1642.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1642.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.threadControl?topicID=1642.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstower